spaghetti with chopped-up hot dogs...

241
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,839
...whenever I wanted, so who cares?

242
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:11,476
Not once did my mother
ever give me any love or affection...

243
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,875
...forjust being myself.
I always had to earn it.

244
00:14:14,079 --> 00:14:16,798
Oh, Leonard, I'm sure
she loves you very much.

245
00:14:16,999 --> 00:14:20,275
In her own cold, godless way.

246
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:24,030
Yeah, and you certainly
don't have to earn my love.

247
00:14:24,199 --> 00:14:26,315
