253
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,592
Come on, she did kind of start it.

254
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:45,394
A good Christian would've
turned the other cheek.

255
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:49,115
On the other hand,
a good Texan would've shot her, so....

256
00:14:51,999 --> 00:14:54,194
I kind of split the difference.

257
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:57,393
Hey, who's in the mood
for spaghetti and hot dogs?

258
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,669
-Oh, me!
-Yeah, me too!

259
00:14:58,879 --> 00:15:00,597
Coming up.

260
00:15:01,199 --> 00:15:03,633
