I need to say to you.

274
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:53,395
Oh, really? That's too bad.

275
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:56,910
Leonard, I always
made you earn my affection...

276
00:15:57,120 --> 00:16:01,079
