more than one way to raise a child.

277
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:03,669
I taught her that.

278
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:07,192
Therefore I would like to
initiate a new protocol...

279
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,708
